{"tid":2438112,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"珉娥自爆中學時遭性侵 怕父母發現唔敢報警","createTime":"2021-03-08T09:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T06:45:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e957052627577595bb430b3b89f156a9b85a3f06","tid":2438112,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WcycbsYGhOFd_EcaB-YKEDkOmYM=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LKDBRSALNVCDJC5LKJGRM2D3HY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWcycbsYGhOFd_EcaB-YKEDkOmYM%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLKDBRSALNVCDJC5LKJGRM2D3HY.jpg&h=d46b9d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新增內容<br />\n<br />\n韓國女團AOA的27歲前成員珉娥，去年7月在網上控訴10年來一直遭隊長智珉欺凌，飽受抑鬱症及恐慌症困擾的她先後三度自殘，又不時在網上放負，令fans非常擔心。昨日珉娥開直播時，更自爆曾在中學時遭男前輩性侵，對方是「只要說出名字就能知道的名人」。<br />\n<br />\n兼職賺生活費<br />\n珉娥表示：「從小學開始家庭生活就很困難，升上初中後就得賺生活費。讀書時因為工作而缺課，因此傳出了很多不好的傳聞。」珉娥透露：「有一次因為朋友說要去某個地方，我很擔心而勸阻對方，然後就一起去了。在空屋內，被大一歲的男生用啤酒樽打中頭部後踢了一腳，然後一直被打。後面有好幾個男生，他們是出名的不良少年。遭性侵後我於離開的路上連行路都行不好，所以像爬一樣回家。如果父母知道的話，可能會發生更嚴重的事，所以沒有報警。因為不想被媽媽發現，所以用衣服遮住了身上的瘀血。」<br />\n<br />\n澄清不是藝人<br />\n珉娥的爆料引起網民熱議後，今日她於直播澄清，指性侵她的人不是藝人，而是類似黑社會的人士，對方是比她大一、兩歲的前輩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/a765Xz-9O0XBGhggl5Zw_9MB3mc=/802x711/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WSNESQHPBNGIFBAEKZXISZEO3I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fa765Xz-9O0XBGhggl5Zw_9MB3mc%3D%2F802x711%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWSNESQHPBNGIFBAEKZXISZEO3I.jpg&h=69fd1430&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ztoq1gV1hnxHFcSU6LKSX04AHXc=/802x959/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BGZBGMPN5FDRDFZOX5HFH2V4LE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZtoq1gV1hnxHFcSU6LKSX04AHXc%3D%2F802x959%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBGZBGMPN5FDRDFZOX5HFH2V4LE.jpg&h=a1ced3cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210308/ZPZFDBKWWVCAJLNGCWMXELLAXI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210308%2FZPZFDBKWWVCAJLNGCWMXELLAXI%2F&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1RvxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=cd7bfc08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210308%2FZPZFDBKWWVCAJLNGCWMXELLAXI%2F&h=78a261b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210308/ZPZFDBKWWVCAJLNGCWMXELLAXI/</a>"},{"pid":"c157f562ab53695fbf50604dc4297c009699ac22","tid":2438112,"uid":255310,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:45:05.000Z","msg":"過氣團又出嚟刷存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c344bbbcc251d62ea2d277ef9af91c822cd39c4d","tid":2438112,"uid":235391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:45:18.000Z","msg":"忍喚 mina chok野 .gif"},{"pid":"f611ae8a97a01252abcfcdb9ca565e63383db830","tid":2438112,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:10:47.000Z","msg":"等我接收佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c1ddbd2d47df7bc068f0e396a72aca6b0c75ec","tid":2438112,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:25:32.000Z","msg":"冇套有冇中愛滋"},{"pid":"f555c565a44058a8255a59d5eeb00a4b1e17253b","tid":2438112,"uid":294121,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:41:55.000Z","msg":"又欺凌又性侵又自殺<br />\n幾時開套戲